<br>
Improved Combat tacits (15 Points) would give you immune to being stunned from the front, iksar ac bonus(35ac or whatever they get at 60), and iksar/troll regen (3points or whatever it is at 60)and everyone gets slam w/o a shield. This would virtually emlimate all the what race is better war type questions and at 15points its costly, but the rewards are worth it. Maybe have it add an innate 10/sta/agi and 25attk to make it more appealing. Again this has to have a steep cost but yield worthy results. ANd it has to be a package deal b/c trolls want to be immune to stun to, eventho they already have the regen and slam...<br>
<br>
Now for general warrior tweaks via AA:<br>
<br>
Improvded Defensive Ability (5) points. When defensive disc is used warrior will hit at 80% of his normal dps, but will proc a +100hate proc untop of whatever weapon proc he may already have. (mini enraging blow type thing). Req ND/CS/CA 3 and AE taunt<br>
<br>
Improvded Defensive tatics (12) points: Will make CS/ND/CA get a 9% bonus. In other words if you have Natural Durabilitty3 it will knock up the bonus to 19% instead of the current 10% Preq CS/ND/CA all at lvl 3. <br>
<br>
Improved Surviability(6): will get 9hp per sta poits instead of 6. This is key, warriors need to have substanitally more HP then pallies/sk's and monkies (since monkies can tank take dmg more or less equal to war w/o defensive). This will give us a strong edge with the HP. Will also get a 3% HP bonus off any buff spells (ie aego will give 1k hp+3% = another 30hp) I notice. <br>
<br>
We absorbe dmg thatis our job,mainly melee dmg but small lil extra edgeover other classes for absorbing dmg....<br>
<br>
Improved Resistance to Mana (5) points:<br>
5 sv to all resitss. Not 5 % but 5 points. <br>
<br>
I dont particulaly care for too much offensive stuff really, not more then what we got already (ambidex, flurry, 2x riposte) while I realize that outside of ambidex the other offensive stuff is very small DPS increase, remeber we are a dmg absorbing class.  <p><center> <img src=http://www.crimsontwilight.org/Upload/Xylor/xylor2.jpg></center> <BR>


